-----------------------
 WSL2
-----------------------
*Enable VT on BIOS

*Enable WSL2

*Download Kali Image(Windows Store)

* Install full tools
sudo apt -y install build-essential
sudo install -y kali-linux-everything
sudo install -y install kali-menu

* xrdp
sudo apt install -y xrdp
service xrdp start

* docker
sudo apt install -y doker

フルインストールすると1時間程度かかったので、VirtualBoxでもよいのかもしれぬ。

-----------------------
 Docker
-----------------------
# pull
https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/kalilinux
docker pull kalilinux/kali-rolling

# update kali and install KDE
apt update
apt install -y kali-defaults kali-root-login desktop-base kde-full

# commit
docker ps
docker start ID
docker attach ID
docker commit ID kali
docker images <- check kali

# port
docker run -it --rm -p 4444:4444 kali

